an class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="快速幂求余"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#快速幂求余"></a> 快速幂求余:</h1><p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msup><mn>3</mn><mrow><mn>2</mn><mn>0</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>9</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mn>0</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>5</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mn>0</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><msup><mo>)</mo><mn>5</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>1</mn><mn>5</mn></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>⇒</mo><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>l</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>∗</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">3^{20}\%4=(9\%4)^{10}\%4=5^{10}\%4=(25\%4)^5\%4=1^5\%4 \Rightarrow result=(1*1)\%4=1</annotation></semantics></math> </span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="strut" style="height:.8141079999999999em"></span> <span class="strut bottom" style="height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-.25em"></span> <span class="base textstyle uncramped"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathrm">3</span> <span class="vlist"><span style="top:-.363em;margin-right:.05em"><span class="fontsize-ensurer reset-size5 size5"><span style="font-size:0">​</span> </span><span class="reset-textstyle scriptstyle uncramped"><span class="mord scriptstyle uncramped"><span class="mord mathrm">2</span> <span class="mord mathrm">0</span> </span></span></span><span class="baseline-fix"><spa